Usage: ORIGNICK on nick [QUIET]|off
  Client will try to switch to nick specified after ON. Use ORIGNTIME
  to define how often it does that. If QUIET is specified messages
  indicating who has your wanted nick will be supressed. Multiple
  nicks can be specified by separating them with comma (example:
  john,doe). Client will use nicks in the specified order.
  
See also:
  ORIGNTIME
